column3: Gegeroon of Memeroon's Trading Post has deliveries that need to be made.
Gegeroon of Memeroon's Trading Post has a delivery to make, but not enough time to do it himself. Help him out and deliver a hot box lunch to Tanga Tonga in his cabin at Thalaos.
Tanga Tonga is immensely pleased to receive his little bag full of toast and egg products. Fully sated, he can now focus on his research.
Deliver the hot box lunch to Tanga Tonga.
Gegeroon has good goods. Good goods need delivery. But Gegeroon busy. Too, too busy.
Have hot box lunch. Qiqirn hot box lunch. Lunch for Tanga Tonga. Tanga Tonga in Thalaos. You take for Gegeroon!
Leave me be. I'm too hungry to continue my research, let alone receive visitors.
This... This is a Qiqirn hot box lunch from Memeroon's Trading Post! H-How did you...? Thank you, friend! At last, I will be able to hear myself think over the growling of my stomach.

I was so eager to come study the fossils, I never gave any thought to how I'd take my meals. I've neither the time nor the materials to cook on my own, so the trading post has been a godssend. I'm always happy to be on the receiving end of a nice, hot box lunch!
